text: Karl Pannos (16 September 1908 - 17 September 1944) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1908 births Category:1944 deaths Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
